snippet.title: Monster Hunter Freedom Unite Trailer
snippet.description:
In the world of Monster Hunter, you are never alone.  Witness the epic struggle to hunt majestic monsters that roam the landscape.  Do you have what it takes to team up with your friends and become the ultimate hunter?
